<subSubSection id="C43A1EEFE9A40289CF8BD986FB021A80" pageId="1" pageNumber="26" type="notes">
<paragraph id="2E41A735D80095FD41B9D7BE16FF5A0D" pageId="1" pageNumber="26">Note.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="91AC7509FFE5CA3F5D97E04C3AB528E0" pageId="1" pageNumber="26">
Italia, Toscana, Monte Argentario (Grosseto province), rocce calcaree nella gariga bassa a erica 
