e rosmarino verso La Ciana fra Punta Avoltore e Punta di Torre Ciana (WGS84: 
<geoCoordinate id="D055D27F7F90171BE3E809CA283985C2" degrees="42" direction="north" minutes="22.25" orientation="latitude" precision="9" value="42.370834">42°22.25'N</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate id="13B00DF814C3C9127191C8B615CBB7BE" degrees="11" direction="east" minutes="09.98" orientation="longitude" precision="9" value="11.166333">11°09.98'E</geoCoordinate>
), 80 m, 23 May 2020, 
<emphasis id="360A45A3CADC74E6A184D2EBF14F446A" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="26">F. Selvi &amp; I. Bettarini</emphasis>
